vibes with classic cruise fun. Guests can unwind at the 5 O'Clock
Somewhere Bar, sip tropical cocktails poolside or enjoy live music in
one of the many onboard lounges. Entertainment includes themed parties,
comedy shows and high-energy performances that celebrate the
Margaritaville lifestyle.<br>
<br>
